    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Shopping List — Mealie → Home Assistant\n\nListens for Mealie event notifications (shopping list item changes)\nand pushes them to the Home Assistant Shopping List integration.\n\n**Webhook:** POST /webhook/mealie-shopping-sync\n\n**Mealie setup required:**\n- Household Settings → Notifications → Create\n- URL: `https://n8n.<env>.thebozic.com/webhook/mealie-shopping-sync`\n- Events: `shopping_list_item.created`, `.updated`, `.deleted`\n\n**Environment variables used:**\n- `HA_URL` — Home Assistant base URL\n- `HOMEASSISTANT_API_TOKEN` — HA Long-Lived Access Token\n\n**Loop prevention:**\n- Items with `extras.synced_from = \"n8n\"` are skipped",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 380
      },
